Package guardians.model.repositories

Contains the repository interfaces used to access the data-source configured.

Package guardians.model.repositories Description

Contains the repository interfaces used to access the data-source configured. Note: the actual classes implementing these interfaces will vary depending on the selected data-source. Nevertheless, they will be auto-generated by Jpa.
Author:
miggoncan
